{"tid":48982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我上lihkg係想討論、吹水，唔係考試！","createTime":"2016-12-21T11:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T01:04:16.000Z","uid":2961,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b1ff00bd66a185ac7fb137e20a6c4edd2a7d19","tid":48982,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"工作已經辛苦，生活壓力大，<br />\n上lihkg想輕鬆一下，但成日擔驚受怕，<br />\n怕寫錯字俾人話用蝗語，又怕唔記得用地道香港字，<br />\n其實為乜？ 我自己都好怕見到咩5p字，覺得中文水準低落，但有陣時見到版友只係錯別字，都俾人鏟到上天，其實又有冇必要？<br />\n簡單提點就得，為乜要成日問候人娘親？"},{"pid":"e78f9f34a112a869ee6ce142a810419213e5e08f","tid":48982,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係壓力大先要屌人老母"},{"pid":"4b772c77a40ba67a0c30564c106835c99a4839a3","tid":48982,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"入鄉隨俗"},{"pid":"447071aa1295e11a0cbb9929790801c79c0b1953","tid":48982,"uid":29086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"你返香土啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069dd3e6aa2032885fd5d94b928f5567b2f93d7f","tid":48982,"uid":19363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"bye 5p仔"},{"pid":"a352fa4bd358282f1816a019de625f6a8f25f91d","tid":48982,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"總有人喜歡做認字特警"},{"pid":"2c8a3a204f92e99bde79eabf068d30b71fa36ed3","tid":48982,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係壓力大先要屌人老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有咁嘅深奧道理？"},{"pid":"2e71fc4511407bc9c8124a03a3848f98f0c1c33f","tid":48982,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bye 5p仔</